The Instituto Mexicano del Seguro Social - IMSS (Social Insurance Institute of Mexico) announced that it is leading a research project to discover the gene for obesity in children and young people under the title "Genetics of Pregnancy in Childhood and Youth", with which the genetic markers should be found in conjunction with overweight.
Miguel Cruz López, Head of the Unidad de Investigación Médica en Biochemica (Department of Medical Research, Biochemistry) at the Hospital de Specialidades del Centro Médico Nacional Siglo XXI, said that an interdisciplinary team consisting of doctors, nurses, nutrition specialists and social workers was established.
This team is supported by specialists and postgraduate students at the Instituto Nacional de Salud Pública (INSP) and the Centro de Investigación y de Estudios Avanzados (Cinvestav) del Instituto Politécnico Nacional (IPN).
